data.description: REFRIGERATOR INCLUDED!!! This end-unit Norris plan has three levels and more than 2,200 square feet! The main floor features a den/flex space, pocket office, and drop zone along with the open family room/kitchen area. All bedrooms are on the second floor, and the third floor has a huge bonus room with more than 350 square feet. The kitchen has stone gray cabinets, quartz counters, a white ceramic tile backsplash in a brick pattern, and stainless appliances, including a gas range. The owner's bedroom is accented with a tray ceiling, and the owner's bath has a tiled, walk-in shower with a bench seat. Other upgrades include a rear covered patio, a double-bowl vanity in the hall bath, metal balusters, and Enhanced Vinyl Plank flooring in the main living areas. Ask about Smart Home features INCLUDED in this home. This wonderful north Charlotte community is located close to major employers and within walking distance to shopping.
